  nameID: Ginjal
  nameEN: Kidney
  kickerID: Sistem ekskresi
  taglineID: Dua penyaring kecil yang menjaga keseimbangan tubuh.
  paragraphID: "Ginjal menyaring darah sekitar 50 kali per hari, membuang limbah
    sebagai urin. Setiap ginjal berisi sekitar satu juta nefron \u2014 unit penyaring
    mikroskopis yang menjaga kadar cairan, elektrolit, dan tekanan darah tetap stabil."
  funfactID: "Ginjal menyaring sekitar 180 liter darah setiap hari \u2014 hampir
    setara tiga drum penuh."
  kickerEN: Excretory
  taglineEN: Two small filters that keep your body in balance.
  paragraphEN: "The kidneys filter blood about 50 times a day, removing waste as
    urine. Each kidney contains around one million nephrons \u2014 microscopic filtering
    units that keep fluid levels, electrolytes, and blood pressure stable."
  funfactEN: "Your kidneys filter roughly 180 litres of blood every day \u2014 nearly
    three full drums."
  facts:
  - labelID: Nefron
    labelEN: Nephrons
    value: ~1 juta/ginjal
  - labelID: Saring/hari
    labelEN: Filter/day
    value: 180 liter
  - labelID: Urin/hari
    labelEN: Urine/day
    value: "1\u20132 liter"
  quiz:
  - questionID: 'Unit penyaring terkecil di dalam ginjal disebut:'
    questionEN: 'The smallest filtering unit inside the kidney is called:'
    answersID:
    - Glomerulus
    - Nefron
    - Ureter
    - Korteks
    answersEN:
    - Glomerulus
    - Nephron
    - Ureter
    - Cortex
    correctIndex: 1
  - questionID: Berapa liter darah yang disaring ginjal per hari?
    questionEN: How many litres of blood do the kidneys filter per day?
    answersID:
    - 5 liter
    - 20 liter
    - 180 liter
    - 500 liter
    answersEN:
    - 5 litres
    - 20 litres
    - 180 litres
    - 500 litres
    correctIndex: 2
  - questionID: 'Produk buangan utama yang dikeluarkan ginjal:'
    questionEN: 'The main waste product expelled by the kidneys:'
    answersID:
    - Karbon dioksida
    - Empedu
    - Urin
    - Keringat
    answersEN:
    - Carbon dioxide
    - Bile
    - Urine
    - Sweat
    correctIndex: 2
